snippet.title: ELDEN RING NIGHTREIGN | Official Pre-Order Trailer
snippet.description:
Remain steadfast against the encroaching rain, Nightfarers.
The Nightlord awaits your arrival.

Make your landfall in Limveld on May 30th, 2025.
Pre-order #ELDENRING #NIGHTREIGN: https://bnent.eu/Preorder-NIGHTREIGN
